	Set default HOMEPAGE to CPAN_AUTHOR's search.cpan.org module page.

	* lib/gnome2.cygclass:
	Set default HOMEPAGE to gnome.org.
	Don't run gnome-doc-prepare when building gnome-doc-utils.

	* bin/cygport.in:
	Add pkg_dist() to packaging stages.
	Check for setup.hint files presence during pkg_dist().
	Avoid recursive directory loops with top-level CYGWIN-PATCHES symlink.
	Create ${S}-orig only if nonexistant.
	Exclude more file patterns from gtk-doc package diffs.
	Localize function variables.

	* bin/prep_libtool_modules.sh:
	Raise error if dynamic module is missing.

	* configure.in: 
	Post-release version bump.

